file i can change:
    assets
    

always do "npx expo install --check" before push to EAS build
    npx expo-doctor@latest
    npx expo install --check


build developmental build on EAS
    eas build --platform android --profile development


to get all dependancies to local mashine:
    npm install
    npx expo prebuild 
    npx expo install  expo-android-usagestats @supersami/rn-foreground-service expo-notifications
    npx expo install expo-router react-native-safe-area-context react-native-screens expo-linking expo-constants expo-status-bar


change expo version(if the current is too new)
    npx expo install expo@51
    npm install expo@~55


remember the popup to guide user to the permission menu
    setting/apps/3 dot at top right coner/special access/user data access
